N2  - The article presents 1963 Academy of Management news briefs. The annual meeting of the Academy featured sessions relating to systems management, developments in personnel administration, and business policy. Officers were elected for the Western Division of the Academy. Among those elected were Keith Davis and Dale Yoder. Dr. E. H. Anderson, professor of management at the University of Alabama, died on July 24, 1963.
